	(text "In the rpi pico datasheet,\nthey specifify a mosfet to\nprevent reverse leakage current\nwhen 3v3 is off but vsys is\npresent due to the 3v3_en pin\nbeing pulled low.\n100k,50k voltage divider = 9.9v max in"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 356.87 97.536 0)
		(effects
